data.description: Welcome to your new home, where warmth and comfort abound! As you step into the two-story entry, youall be greeted by an inviting atmosphere. The gourmet kitchen is a chefas delight, featuring granite countertops, stained cabinets, and stainless-steel appliances a the heart of the home where memories are made.  Entertain effortlessly in the separate dining room and unwind in the large living room, complete with a wood-burning fireplace for those cozy evenings. Step outside to the impressive, covered entertainment patio, featuring concrete pavers and a large gas fire pit surrounded by custom stonework.  Privacy curtains and a TV mount make this the perfect haven for relaxation and gatherings. Upstairs youall find a spacious primary bedroom, offering a homeowneras retreat with trey ceiling and a large ensuite bath complete with garden tub, separate shower, double vanity, and granite countertops. Discover three generously sized secondary bedrooms, providing plenty of space for family and guests. The front porch, adorned with solid cedar posts and beams beneath a tongue-and-groove ceiling adds a touch of charm to your homeas faAade.  Professionally landscaped grounds with rubber mulch and an irrigation system ensure a lush and low-maintenance environment.  As a resident, enjoy the community pool for a refreshing escape on sunny days. This home invites you to embrace a lifestyle of warmth, simplicity, and joyful living. Welcome to your new home!
